title: The Amazing Digital Circus Just CLOWNED on Us 🤡 #shorts
description:
Hear us out… Jack Black of @JablinskiGames will be a giant monster in the new hit YouTube show by @GLITCH The Amazing Digital Circus. Why do we think that? Well, after clicking a parody link in the Digital Circus pilot, we found a menacingly fun ARG hunt. And all of the clues lead to Jack Black voicing an upcoming character called Kaufmo.
